attributes.Long form description: The student is screwing a shelf together. He starts by aligning the tray with its longest side standing up, and then he aligns the first leg with the bottom. They screw the first screw of the first leg, and then he screws the first screw of the second leg, and then he screws a second screw onto the second leg, and then he screws a second screw onto the first leg. He turns the tray around and screw both screws onto the third leg, and then
